text: Komyshuvakha may refer to the following Ukrainian localities: * Komyshuvakha, Donetsk Oblast, an urban-type settlement in Donetsk Oblast; * Komyshuvakha, Zaporizhia Oblast, an urban-type settlement in Zaporizhia Oblast; * Komyshuvakha, Luhansk Oblast, an urban-type settlement in Luhansk Oblast.
title: Komyshuvakha
